<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>WattzUp - Home Energy Analyzer</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"/>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>WattzUp</h1>
      <p>Take charge of your electricity. Measure, manage, and save on home energy costs.</p>
      <a href="#tool" class="cta-btn">Start Calculating</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section id="tool" class="tool-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>🧮 Appliance Power Consumption Calculator</h2>
      <form id="calc-form">
        <label for="power">Power Rating (W):</label>
        <input type="number" id="power" required>

        <label for="hours">Hours Used Per Day:</label>
        <input type="number" id="hours" required>

        <label for="days">Number of Days:</label>
        <input type="number" id="days" required>

        <label for="rate">Electricity Rate ($/kWh):</label>
        <input type="number" step="0.01" id="rate" required>

        <button type="submit">Calculate Cost</button>
      </form>

      <div id="result" class="result-box"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="info-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>💡 Energy-Smart Appliance Recommendations</h2>
      <p>Based on your home's energy profile, we suggest energy-efficient alternatives to help you reduce your electricity bill.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🏠 Small Apartment: Low-wattage induction cooktops, compact inverter fridges</li>
        <li>🏡 Medium Home: Energy Star-rated washing machines, smart thermostats</li>
        <li>🏘️ Large Home: Solar-compatible systems, zoned HVAC setups</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2025 WattzUp. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="script.js.WattzUp"></script>
</body>
</html>
